
App does the following:
1)Upload Job description.
2)Upload Profiles
3)Screen profiles
4)Display result of candidates
5)Compares profiles based on skillsets
6)Filters profiles based on skillset
7)Used Redis via brew for better caching


                   +---------------------+
Upload JD + Resumes
                   |
                   v
          Resume Parser Service
                   |
                   v
         Vector Embedding Service
          (OpenAI / BGE / Instructor)
                   |
                   v
        Vector Database (FAISS/Pinecone)
                   |
                   v
       Similarity Search (Top K resumes)
                   |
                   v
           LLM Screening Agents
                   |
                   v
        Ranking + Risk + Interview Insights
                   |
                   v
              React UI



Upload 1000 resumes
        ↓
Parser service extracts text
        ↓
Embedding generation
        ↓
Vector similarity search
        ↓
Top 50 resumes
        ↓
Async LLM screening
        ↓
Ranking
        ↓
Results streamed to UI




Upload JD + Resumes
        │
        ▼
Resume Parser
        │
        ▼
Redis Cache Check
        │
 ┌──────┴──────┐
 │             │
Cache Hit   Cache Miss
 │             │
Return      LLM Evaluation
 │             │
 └──────┬──────┘
        ▼
Results Stored in Redis
        ▼
Ranking
